<BODY BGCOLOR = #ffffff>

<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="/Images/cc_headr.gif" ALT="Working Icon">
<IMG SRC="/images/working.gif" ALT="Cover Crop Icon  " ALIGN="right">
<BR CLEAR=all><HR>
<CENTER><TABLE WIDTH=500 BORDER=10>
<TH COLSPAN=2><FONT SIZE="+2"><I>Images of Clovers (Trifolium)</I></FONT></TD>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=2><B>Note: </B>The following cover crop images are part of an extensive collection of cover crop images maintained by several members of the UC SAREP staff.  The images have not been completely categorized and labeled.  We are currently working on providing a select few of these images for a book on cover crops, but all images have been made available online because of the overwhelming number of requests we have had for them.</TD><TR>
