<DOCOLDNO>IA051-000874-B008-100</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sarep.ucdavis.edu:80/SAREP/NEWSLTR/v3n2/sa-14.htm 198.31.121.163 19970210155902 text/html 8568
