<p>In FY 1994/95, five more graduate students were awarded a total of $7,973.
The students and the titles of their projects are: </p>

<ul>
<p><b>Heinrich Schweizer</b>, Department of Entomology, UC Davis, $2,000
for &quot;Identification of Non-Pesticidal Mortality Factors of Scirtothrips
