<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Cover Crop Database: Complete Crop Summary of Meadow Barley</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR = #ffffff>

<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="/Images/cc_headr.gif" ALT="Working Icon">
<IMG SRC="/images/working.gif" ALT="Cover Crop Icon  " ALIGN="right">
<BR CLEAR=all><HR>
<A HREF = "#top"></A><H1>Meadow Barley</H1><HR>
<B><DL><DT><A HREF="/cgi-win/ccrop.exe/show_imgs_24">Images of Meadow Barley</A></B><BR></DL>
<B><DT>Maximum Height</B>
<DD>Height for meadow barley was 70.49+/-5.43 cm (Mean +/- S.E.M.), at the Blue Heron Vineyard (Fetzer Vineyards), Hopland, Mendocino County, California, on May 2, 1991 (Bugg et al., unpublished data).<P>
<B><DT>Biomass</B>
<DD>Above-ground biomass of meadow barley was 3.712+/-0.445 Mg/ha, Mean +/- S.E.M., at the Blue Heron Vineyard (Fetzer Vineyards), Hopland, Mendocino County, California, May 2, 1991.  Total above-ground biomass data (dry, cover crop + weeds) was 5.912+/-1.330 (Mg/ha, Mean +/- S.E.M.) (Bugg et al., unpublished data).<P>
<B><DT>Pest Effects, Weeds</B>
<DD>Weed above-ground biomass data (dry) was 2.199+/-1.228 Mg/ha, Mean +/- S.E.M.  in plots seeded to meadow barley the previous October, Blue Heron Vineyard (Fetzer Vineyards), Hopland, Mendocino County, California.  Cover crops were seeded in late October, 1990; harvest was on May 15-16, 1991. Dominant winter annual weeds were chickweed, shepherds purse, rattail fescue, and annual ryegrass (Bugg et al., unpublished data).<P> Percentage of vegetational cover by meadow barley on May 2 was 53.75+/-7.47 (Mean +/- S.E.M.) (Bugg et al., unpublished data).<P>
</DL><B><I><A HREF = "#top"> To top of Meadow Barley</A></B></I><P>
<PRE>

</PRE><A HREF="/sarep/ccrop/ccrop.map">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/images/CC_Footer.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=486 HEIGHT=63 ALT="Cover Crop Database Footer Image" ISMAP></A>
