<h2 align=center>University of California 
<br>Sustainable Agriculture Research and Education Program </h2>

<center><p><img src="/sarep/pubs/progressreport/images/93-95Progreport.gif" alt="Image: 1993-1995 Progress Report" border=0 height=90 width=323></p></center>

<h3 align=center>UC Sustainable Agriculture Research and Education Program

<br>University of California, Davis, CA 95616 
