<h2 align=center>1995 GRANTS FOR EDUCATIONAL EVENTS </h2>

<ul>
<p><b>Thistle Management in California</b>. Michael Smith, UC Cooperative
Extension, San Luis Obispo County. $1,000 </p>

<p><b>Agroforestry Technology Course</b>. Miles Merwin, International Tree
Crops Institute, Davis. $1,000 </p>

<p><b>Development of Comparative Crop Systems Research Projects in the
Central San Joaquin Valley</b>: Farmer/Scientist Focus Session to Identify
Research Priorities and Appropriate Cropping Systems Research Options.
Jeff Mitchell, Department of Vegetable Crops, UC Davis. $424 </p>

<p><b>Demonstrating Improved Rangeland Management for Improving Water Quality</b>.
Stephanie Larson, UC Cooperative Extension, Marin County. $1,000 </p>

